<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Waste Request Collection Confirmation - Waste Zero</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #888888;
            padding: 20px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Waste Request Collection Confirmed</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>We are pleased to inform you that your waste request has been successfully collected.</p>

            <p><strong>Details of your request:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Waste Category:</strong> <%= wasteCategory %></li>
                <li><strong>Quantity:</strong> <%= quantity %> kg</li>
                <li><strong>Estimated Price:</strong> LKR <%= estimatedPrice %></li>
                <li><strong>Confirmation Date:</strong> <%= confirmationDate %></li>
            </ul>

            <p>Thank you for using Waste Zero for your waste management needs. If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
